name: The Core of a Star #3
description:
The very core of what we are,
they say is similar to a star.
Water and blood, globules of mud,
the colorful heart; its excited thud.
Imagination flowing brightly.
Visions in mind appearing nightly.
Make from life what you will.
Feel its essence; that feather-like thrill.
You're more than just rules written in books.
Like a fish you avoid the hooks.
Dargonflies, bees, turbulant seas.
The light called 'home' 
to where your soul flees.
Utopia is here already!
Just remember to keep going steady.
